Package no.uio.ifi.clearinghouse

Enum Clearinghouse

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Clearinghouse>
no.uio.ifi.clearinghouse.Clearinghouse
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Clearinghouse>, Constable
public enum Clearinghouse
extends Enum<Clearinghouse>
Singleton class to to be used for getting visa JWT tokens provided access JWT token and for converting visa JWT tokens to Visa POJOs.

    • getVisas

      public Collection<Visa> getVisas​(String accessToken, String openIDConfigurationURL)
      Validates access JWT token and returns a list of Visas obtained from "/userinfo" endpoint. Access token is validated based on JWKs URL of the OpenID configuration. Visa tokens are validated based on JKUs.
      Parameters:
      accessToken - Access JWT token.
      openIDConfigurationURL - ".well-known/openid-configuration" full URL.
      Returns:
      List of GA4GH Visas.

    • getVisasWithPEMPublicKey

      public Collection<Visa> getVisasWithPEMPublicKey​(String accessToken, String pemPublicKey)
      Validates access JWT token and returns a list of Visas obtained from "/userinfo" endpoint. Access token is validated based on PEM RSA public key provided. Visa tokens are validated based on JKUs.
      Parameters:
      accessToken - Access JWT token.
      pemPublicKey - PEM RSA public key.
      Returns:
      List of GA4GH Visas.

    • getVisasWithPublicKey

      public Collection<Visa> getVisasWithPublicKey​(String accessToken, RSAPublicKey publicKey)
      Validates access JWT token and returns a list of Visas obtained from "/userinfo" endpoint. Access token is validated based on RSA public key provided. Visa tokens are validated based on JKUs.
      Parameters:
      accessToken - Access JWT token.
      publicKey - RSA public key.
      Returns:
      List of GA4GH Visas.

    • getVisa

      public Optional<Visa> getVisa​(String visaToken)
      Validates visa JWT token and converts it to Visa POJO. Token is validated based on JKU.
      Parameters:
      visaToken - Visa JWT token.
      Returns:
      Optional Visa POJO: present if token validated successfully.
